  "original_title": "\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bb8\u0bc8 \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9  \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Federation received a written commitment to support Dulles",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been confirmed that a written document has been received from Tamil National Federation Dulles Akahaperuma and Opposition Leader Sajith Premadasa to vote in favor of the new Interim Presidential candidate Dalles Akhalaperuma today.",
        "Controversies have arisen as to whether or not the Tamil National Federation has received a written document stipulating the conditions for supporting the new interim presidential candidate, Dulles Akazhapperu.",
        "Its spokesperson Sumanthran MP had announced that 'Tamil National Federation has taken a unanimous decision to support the new interim president Dulles Akazhaperuma'.",
        "However, when asked whether a written agreement had been obtained, he said, 'I cannot answer at this time.'",
        "In this case, the English media Daily Mirror has reported that Dulles Alagaperuma and Sajith Premadasa have given a written commitment to the federation.",
        "Following this, Sumanthran denied the news and said in his Twitter post that the news was planned to affect the success of the Dulles beauty.",
        "In this case, Veerakesari, while interacting with the other members who participated in the said meeting, seven members mentioned that 'written assurance was given focusing on ten main and four sub-issues covering the immediate and long-term problems of the Tamil people'.",
        "At the same time, it has been mentioned that 'the relevant document was handed over to Sambandhan by Sajith and Dulles, and Sambandhan handed over the document to Sumandran'.",
        "Also, the said seven members said, 'We had decided to remain neutral during the new interim presidential poll. However, as Sajith personally visited Dallas and gave assurances, we agreed to support them.",
        "At the same time, it is to be noted that even when the president of the Federation tried to contact Sampanthan before the publication of this news, the effort was not successful."
      ],
